  * Upload to unstable. (Closes: #811432)
  * New upstream release.
  * Update watch file.
  * Update Vcs-* fields.
  * Update copyright.
  * Pass -DFOUNDATION_BUILD=OFF to cmake to enforce it, to make sure resources
